                                    <article>
                                        <p>The U.S. has already started to take data compliance more seriously with the enactment of the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA). The CCPA acts similarly in California to the way GDPR does to the EU. Experts predict at least 10 more states will soon follow suit in adopting their own data privacy laws. </p>
                                    </article>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-12">
