                                    <article>
                                        <p>An increasing number of EU based customers in America and vice versa makes it a priority for companies to get familiarised with the new policy and act accordingly. If you are a company that deals with European clientele often, it is imperative that you make the switch to GDPR compliance immediately. </p>
                                    </article>
