                                    <article>
                                        <p>The best method of complying with GDPR regulations is to keep all your sensitive data in one  secure location - A&nbsp;<apex:outputLink style="font-size:16px;" value="{!URLFOR($Page.BN_PMS)}">property management system</apex:outputLink>. Salesforce is one of the most trusted companies when it comes to this, because their platform is built specifically to help companies and boost their revenue. Booking Ninjas shares this use case and we have a genuine, vested interest in the success of our customers, and safety is paramount to that success.</p>
                                    </article>
